HEADWORD: Hylotheism
<hw>Hy"lo*the*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ wood,
matter + <?/ God.]</ety> <def>The doctrine of belief that matter is God,
or that there is no God except matter and the universe; pantheism. See
<er>Materialism</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hylotheist</ent>⟦br⟧
